                                         CAPE TOWN - President Jacob Zuma will be delivering his annual address to the National Council of Provinces (NCOP) this afternoon.  He is expected to provide an update on the progress made in the past year in improving South Africans’ quality of life especially the poor. WATCH: President Zuma delivers annual address in the NCOP 